Package: rapidfire
Type: Package
Title: relatively accurate particulate information derived from inputs retrieved easily
Version: 2.0.1
Author: Sean Raffuse
Maintainer: Sean Raffuse <sraffuse@ucdavis.edu>
Description: Tools for acquiring input data, developing regression models, and using those models to estimate surface level PM2.5 concentrations, especially during wildfire smoke episodes.
